18 million years ago and regrew the vision-related

00:00:11.509 --> 00:00:14.980
parts and increased the size of their brains.

00:00:14.980 --> 00:00:19.680
And researchers from Massachusetts General
Hospital are working on regenerating functional

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:24.480
